## 📸 Reel Feature Highlights

- **Seamless Shopping Experience**: Users discover products through engaging video content and add to cart instantly
- **Seller Benefits**: Higher conversion rates through visual storytelling
- **Modern UI/UX**: Smooth scrolling, auto-play, and intuitive controls
- **Performance Optimized**: Lazy loading, video compression, and efficient caching

